FBIS4-34431 "drlat118_c_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-118 Daily Report 18 Jun 1994 MEXICO Appoints Spokesman for Chiapas Peace Efforts Appoints Spokesman for Chiapas Peace Efforts PA1806143494 Mexico City XEW Television Network in Spanish 0430 GMT 18 Jun 94 PA1806143494 Mexico City XEW Television Network Spanish BFN [From the "24 Hours" newscast] [Text] Today, President Carlos Salinas de Gortari appointed Hector Hernandez Llamas as executive spokesman for the Chiapas peace efforts, which is a recently established position. In order to carry out his duties, Mr. Hernandez Llamas will have to coordinate with Chiapas Governor Javier Lopez Moreno who has become responsible for conducting all efforts related to the peace process.
